OL,3,CNHS Borders call crisis meeting to
OL,4,Cplug #30 million deficit
OL,6,FHealth bosses at NHS Borders have said
OL,7,Ffrontline services will be impacted as
OL,8,Fthey try to find ways to save more
OL,9,Fmoney than ever before.
OL,11,FThe board has a deficit of almost
OL,12,F#30million and has called an emergency
OL,13,Fmeeting with the Scottish Government
OL,14,Fto discuss its options.
OL,16,FThe public have been told to expect to
OL,17,Fsee frontline services, hospital beds,
OL,18,Fand the workforce impacted in the year
OL,19,Fahead.
