OL,3,CNHS Borders call crisis meeting to
OL,4,Cplug #30 million deficit
OL,6,FIn a public meeting of the board,
OL,7,FChief Executive Ralph Roberts admitted
OL,8,FthatJthe level of savings they need to
OL,9,Fmake is unprecedented, and still
OL,10,Fdoesn't go far enough.
OL,12,F"The level of savings that we've
OL,13,Fidentified is twice the amount we've
OL,14,Fever delivered in a year before, and
OL,15,Fthat maybe sets out the scale of the
OL,16,Fchallenge," he said.
OL,18,F"But we're obviously also
OL,19,Facknowledging that doesn't take us far
OL,20,Fenough.
