OL,6,F"We're starting the year with a 28
OL,7,Fmillion pound deficit if we don't add
OL,8,Fin the additional costs we expect to
OL,9,Fincur next year," he said.
OL,11,F"If we did nothing else, we would
OL,12,Foverspend by 40 million pounds."
OL,14,FWith savings tallied up, the health
OL,15,Fboard still projects it will end the
OL,16,Fyear with an overspend of 25 million
OL,17,Fpounds, which is "certainly not where
OL,18,Fwe would want to be," he said.
