OL,6,FNHS Borders Director of Finance Andrew
OL,7,FBone has said the key issue at the
OL,8,Fmoment is thatJthey're "unable to
OL,9,Fprovide a financial plan which
OL,10,Fbalances for the year ahead."
OL,12,FUnable to balance the books, means
OL,13,Fthat savings will need to be made in
OL,14,F"every part of theJorganisation."
