OL,6,F"The savings are coming out across the
OL,7,Fwhole of our service, it will need to
OL,8,Fcome out of our workforce, and that
OL,9,Fwill be about looking at the type of
OL,10,Fworkforce we have, reducing things
OL,11,Flike agency spend and overtime,"
OL,12,Fcontinued Ralph Roberts.
OL,14,F"We need to be honest in the NHS, 75%
OL,15,Fof our cost is staff.
OL,17,F"There is no way we'll make the level
OL,18,Fof savings required if we continue to
OL,19,Fincrease theJnumber of staff that
OL,20,Fwe've got and we will have to look at
OL,21,Fhow we can reduce."
