OL,6,FHe assured there would be no
OL,7,Fcompulsory redundancies.
OL,9,FHe also said they need to look at the
OL,10,Fnumber of beds in the system and will
OL,11,Fwork with other agencies to see how
OL,12,Fpeople can be cared for at home or in
OL,13,Fthe community as opposed to in a
OL,14,Fhospital setting.
